1
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:25,700
父亲 我的父亲 你在船上吗
Vater. Mein Vater, bist du an Bord?

2
00:00:27,980 --> 00:00:30,060
爸爸，您在这里吗
Vater, bist du hier?

3
00:00:30,060 --> 00:00:32,340
爸爸
Vater.

4
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:34,180
爸爸！
Vater!

5
00:00:36,060 --> 00:00:39,620
该死……真他妈的该死！
Bloody hell... Bloody, bloody hell!

6
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:55,540
医生说 没有尸体他不来
The doctor says he won't come until he has a body, sir.

7
00:00:55,540 --> 00:00:58,380
什么 什么 他认为底下就只眼球而已？
What? What, he thinks it's just an eyeball down there?

8
00:00:58,380 --> 00:01:00,780
有人靠着码头掉下去了？
Somebody leaned over the quay and it dropped out?

9
00:01:00,780 --> 00:01:03,620
他说死要见尸 头儿
He says he needs a body, sir.

10
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:04,860
不可理喻
Unbelievable.

11
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:10,220
这儿有点东西 就在这儿 警长 警长！是 好的
I've got something here. Right here, Sarge. Sarge! Right, good.

12
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:11,940
跟他说我们有了
Tell him we've got one.

13
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,780
要通知詹特利总督察吗
Shouldn't we call out Chief Inspector Gently?

14
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:19,980
不必 他休息 好了
No, no. He's on leave. Right.

15
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:22,260
继续 医生
Go on, Doctor.

16
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,100
请让一让 往后站站
Please let me through. Stand back.

17
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:47,060
但我得和一把手谈谈
But then I need to talk to whoever is in charge.

18
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:50,860
呃 谁是管事的 没事了 我就是 有何贵干
Well, who is in charge? It's all right, I'm in charge. How can I help?

19
00:01:50,860 --> 00:01:53,740
昨晚起我就没见着我父亲 好了
I am missing my father since last night. OK, right.

20
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:59,740
我们在这儿碰面 一起上船 我就听说水里有具尸体
Since we are to come here, to meet and go on our boat and I am hearing now there is a body in the water!

21
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:01,580
呃 是 请问尊姓大名 先生
Er, yeah. Can I take your name please, sir?

22
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:04,340
威尔海姆・史迈克……我父亲叫冈特・史迈克
Wilhelm Schmeikel...and my father is Gunter Schmeikel.

23
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:05,860
冈特・史迈克
Gunter Schmeikel.

24
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:08,940
我是警探长约翰・巴克斯
I'm Detective Sergeant John Bacchus.

25
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:12,180
-那边的船是你的吗 先生？-求你了
Now, is that your boat over there, sir? Please.

26
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:15,220
我没必要跟你说 我要和长官谈
I have no need to talk to you... I wish to speak to the commanding officer.

27
00:02:15,220 --> 00:02:20,820
-我是负责人 史迈克先生 -你？-是 -不 区区一个警长？
I am in charge, Mr Schmeikel. You? Yeah. No. A mere sergeant?

28
00:02:20,820 --> 00:02:23,020
警探长 实际上
Detective sergeant, actually.

29
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:25,220
不不不……你不明白
No, no no...you do not understand.

30
00:02:25,220 --> 00:02:29,140
-我父亲失踪了 他是重要人物 非常重要 -是 我们尽力
My father is missing. He's an important man, very important. Yeah. We'll try our best.

31
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:36,460
不不 还不够好 无法接受…… 威尔海姆！那是冈特
No, no. That's not good enough. It's unacceptable... Wilhelm! Das ist Gunter.

32
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:41,300
先生 先生 先生 求你了 我要…… 抱歉 亲爱的
Sir. Sir, sir. Please, I need to... Excuse me, sorry, pet.

33
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:43,380
你能告诉我那个被找到的男人……
Can you just tell me the man that's been recovered...

34
00:02:43,380 --> 00:02:47,220
是我的岳父…… 威尔海姆的父亲
Is my father-in-law... It's Wilhelm's father...

35
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:50,540
冈特・史迈克！冈特・史迈克
Gunter Schmeikel! Gunter Schmeikel.

36
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:56,700
为什么不叫我
Why didn't you call me?

37
00:02:56,700 --> 00:03:00,100
因为三十分钟前它只是个不明眼球
Because 30 seconds ago it was just an unidentified eyeball.

38
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:02,220
我以为你休息呢
I thought you were on leave?

39
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:05,820
现在不了 不了 好吧 好吧
Not now, I'm not. Right. Right.

40
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:07,900
那么 有我的事了吗
Is there anything I can do, then?

41
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,060
敢情来杯茶？
Get you a cup of tea, perhaps?

42
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:13,180
不 谢了 看尸体
No, thanks. Look at the body.

43
00:03:13,180 --> 00:03:16,700
呃 眼球被渔民钩出来了
Well, the eyeball was hooked out by a fisherman.

44
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:18,540
不是说眼球 重点错 警长
Not talking about the eyeball, Sergeant.

45
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:24,860
他扭曲得没人形了 是 会到那步的 看他的手 看到什么没
He's all twisted. Yeah, we'll get to that. Look at his hands. What do you see?

46
00:03:26,540 --> 00:03:28,980
没 表明什么
Nothing. What's that tell you?

47
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:30,940
他没做挣扎
He didn't struggle.

48
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:35,420
是 因为如果试图逃生的话他会把手撕碎的 但他没有
Yeah, because he would have torn his hands to shreds trying to get out of here, but he didn't.

49
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:37,300
把他翻个身
Turn him over.

50
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:40,340
把夹克和衬衫拉上来
Pull up his jacket and shirt.

51
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:46,740
脊椎断了
That spine's been snapped.

52
00:03:46,740 --> 00:03:50,980
没挣扎是因为他在这一重击下瘫痪了
He didn't struggle because the attack paralysed him.

53
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:55,980
-意思是他在入水前还是活着的 -正确
Meaning he was alive when he entered the water. Correct.

54
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:58,260
叫医生别来了吗
？Shall I call off the doctor, then?

55
00:03:58,260 --> 00:04:02,140
我来推定死亡时间 赌一把？
I'll have a stab at the time of death, if you like. You fancy a bet?

56
00:04:02,140 --> 00:04:03,780
十或十二个小时
Ten or twelve hours.

57
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:05,300
好吧 算上我了
All right, you're on.

58
00:04:06,940 --> 00:04:11,260
-所以你就是路过 是吧？-呃 你知道的
So you were just passing then, were you? Well, you know.

59
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:13,700
我在车站扫了一眼 是的
I had a look in at the station, yeah.

60
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:15,820
那周你休假？
On your week off?

61
00:04:15,820 --> 00:04:17,820
我们有人了吗
We got a name yet?

62
00:04:17,820 --> 00:04:20,500
是的 冈特・史迈克
Yeah. Gunter Schmeikel.

63
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:24,380
那是什么 德国人 澳洲佬 还是瑞士的
What's that, German, Austrian, Swiss?

64
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:26,220
呃 反正不是东北人 是不
Well, it's not Geordie, is it?

65
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:29,420
泰勒正在跟他的儿子儿媳说话
Taylor's talking to his son and his daughter-in-law...

66
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:31,780
他们估计那儿的船是他的
They reckon that's his boat over there.

67
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:33,740
干得漂亮
Very nice.

68
00:04:36,420 --> 00:04:38,380
钱包呢还是现金？
Any wallet or cash?

69
00:04:38,380 --> 00:04:40,060
没 只有这个
No. Just this.

70
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:46,300
肯定花了不少钱 这个
Must've cost a few bob, this.

71
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:48,220
有些还好
All right for some.

72
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:51,020
我想他们战败了
I thought they lost the war.

73
00:05:09,900 --> 00:05:12,180
值班簿
Log book.

74
00:05:14,580 --> 00:05:19,060
上面说他六天前离开汉堡了
It says here they left Hamburg six days ago.

75
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:21,140
我德语O级
I did German 'O' level.

76
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:22,700
全班领先
Top of me class.

77
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:24,900
哟 那我可松了口气
Well, that's a relief.

78
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:29,140
冈特・史迈克名下的护照
Passport in the name of Gunter Schmeikel.

79
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,900
是他 好的
It's him, all right.

80
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:36,980
旅行袋 看看有没有钱包
Overnight bag. See if there's a wallet.

81
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:43,500
没没 没有
No. No, there isn't.

82
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:51,060
嘿 呃 听着 我17岁时有个德国笔友 从杜塞尔多夫过来了
Hey, eh, listen, I had this German pen pal that came over to stay from Dusseldorf when I was 17.

83
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,980
艾柯 她的名字
Elke, she was called.

84
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:56,220
啊 她……头发到这儿
Ah, man, she was... Hair down to here.

85
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:57,860
天使脸蛋
Face like an angel.

86
00:05:57,860 --> 00:06:00,340
上帝 她真，真是美啊
God, she was, she was beautiful.

87
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:01,900
好
Good.

88
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:06,540
我带他的儿子儿媳和回旅馆 先生
I took the son and daughter-in-law back to their hotel, sir...

89
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:08,700
在山上一里左右 你让他俩落单了？
About a mile up the hill. You left them on their own?

90
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:12,100
你从未说过他们是嫌疑人啊 好吧他们当然是 
You never said they were suspects. Well, of course they're suspects, man.

91
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:14,900
那帮家伙当中有人说死者
Some folks in the crowd said that the deceased was drinking

92
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:19,780
昨晚和一些当地人在海员休息室喝酒 好样的 泰勒
with some locals in the Mariner's Rest last night. Well done, Taylor.

93
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:21,980
我们用你的车
We'll use your car.

94
00:06:29,820 --> 00:06:33,540
呃 你怎么把婴儿车塞进名爵的
Well, how do you fit a pram into an MG?

95
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:36,660
塞不下就不要硬撑
Three into two does not go.

96
00:06:36,660 --> 00:06:38,580
我数学什么的都过了
I did 'O' Level Maths an' all.

97
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:53,660
史迈克夫人在咖啡厅 还有……
Mrs Schmeikel's in the coffee lounge, and...

98
00:06:53,660 --> 00:06:56,620
是的 史迈克先生还在自己的房间里……打电话
Yes. Mr Schmeikel's still in his room...on the phone.

99
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:59,340
-房号？-14
Room number? 14.

100
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:01,020
你不介意我听吧 头儿？
D'you mind if I listen in, Guv?

101
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:04,540
抱歉 我没听清 给我耳麦好吗 有劳了 亲爱的
I'm sorry, I didn't quite catch that. Can I have the headphones, please, pet?

102
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:11,620
谢了
Thanks.

103
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:13,140
行
Yep.

104
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:15,180
什么
What?

105
00:07:15,180 --> 00:07:18,020
他在说德语 他和另一个男人
He's speaking in German. Him and another man.

106
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:21,180
说什么
Saying what?

107
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:24,540
这个嘛有点难度 在你看不到唇部动作的时候
Well, it's a bit tricky, isn't it, when you can't see the lips moving?

108
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:27,780
或者是因为说话的人没长一张天使脸蛋？
Or if the speaker doesn't have the face of an angel?

109
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,420
麻烦打断他
Interrupt him, please.

110
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:33,260
告诉他詹特利总督察想和他谈谈 就现在
Tell him Detective Inspector Gently would like to speak to him. Right now.

111
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:35,140
去叫他
Go and get him.

112
00:07:35,140 --> 00:07:36,740
史迈克先生？
Mr Schmeikel?

113
00:07:36,740 --> 00:07:39,180
是的 有位詹特利探长找
Yes, I have a Detective Gently for yer.

114
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:44,460
总探长 这才像话
Chief Inspector. This is more like it.

115
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:46,260
无意冒犯 警长
No offence intended, Sergeant.

116
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:48,780
好了 詹特利总探长
Right. Chief Inspector Gently.

117
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:50,820
是……谢谢
Yes... Thank you.

118
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:52,700
现在你可以走了 
You can leave now.

119
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:54,140
我们……？
Shall we...?

120
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:57,220
我父亲整晚都在和他所谓的……
My father had been drinking all evening with his so-called...

121
00:07:57,220 --> 00:08:03,940
朋友们喝酒……然后我就想他是不是想到小船里去……还有
friends...and, I'm imagining him trying to get into the dinghy...and, well,

122
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:10,180
他进去了 如果我告诉你们我们觉得他的背断了呢
in he goes. What if I told you we think his back was broken?

123
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:12,140
亲爱的上帝啊
Lieber Gott.

124
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:14,940
-你没事吧 史迈克夫人？-没事
Are you all right, Mrs Schmeikel? Yes.

125
00:08:14,940 --> 00:08:18,660
现在 你提到过你父亲来头不小
Now, you mentioned that your father was important.

126
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:21,420
他在不来梅市有一家大型制药公司
He owns a large pharmaceutical company in Bremen.

127
00:08:21,420 --> 00:08:23,220
那就让他变得重要了？
That makes him important, does it?

128
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:29,220
能告诉我你的手是怎么回事吗 史迈克先生？
Can you tell me what happened to your hands, Mr Schmeikel?

129
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:35,260
这个 这是在北海不擅航行付出的代价
This. This you get from the North Sea when you're no good at sailing!

130
00:08:35,260 --> 00:08:38,100
荒谬！整个一出闹剧！
Ridiculous! This whole thing is ridiculous.

131
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:41,660
哪里荒谬了 先生？
Ridiculous in what way, sir?

132
00:08:41,660 --> 00:08:45,860
我父亲 他 呃 是一名战犯 在44年空战中被击落……
My father, he, er, was a prisoner of war...shot down in '44...

133
00:08:45,860 --> 00:08:48,060
德国空军……轰炸机飞行员……
Luftwaffe...a bomber pilot...

134
00:08:49,540 --> 00:08:52,780
然后就获编了？
and, then... billeted?

135
00:08:52,780 --> 00:08:54,820
获编了 对
Billeted, yeah.

136
00:08:54,820 --> 00:09:02,380
在一家农场里获编排住下了……显然 20年后我必须去拜访投宿 以便能“学会”
Billeted, yes, on a pig farm...which 20 years later I apparently must visit and stay at so I can "learn"

137
00:09:02,380 --> 00:09:06,260
如何经营养猪场
how pig farmers do business...

138
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:10,300
所以我父亲 他待在农场……然后
So my father, he stays on the farm...and

139
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:13,740
-我们来这儿 你和你父亲就这事争执过吗
-we come here. Did you argue with your father over this?

140
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:16,420
他们无时不吵 这……
They argue all the time, it's...

141
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:19,980
这些养猪场农民 就是昨晚和他在酒吧的那些朋友吗
These pig farmers, are they the friends he was in the pub with last night?

142
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:22,900
哈德门一家 是！哈德门一家
The Hardyments, yeah! The Hardyments.

143
00:09:30,820 --> 00:09:34,900
冈特 冈特 过来 咱们唱首虫歌 唱虫歌
Gunter, Gunter. C'mon, let's do the worm song. Do the worm song.

144
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:36,780
不不不 我记不得了
No, no, no, I can't remember it!

145
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:42,260
你当然记得！谁教你的 嗯？走开 老兄 让我们时光倒流二十年！
Course yer can! Who taught yer, eh? Away, man, let's wind the clock back 20 year!

146
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:47,820
别出声 伙计们 吸口气 让我告诉你一件可怕的事
?Whisht lads, hold yer gobs I'll tell yer all an awful story,

147
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:53,820
别出声 伙计们 吸口气 让我告诉你踢走虫子的事
?Whisht lads, hold yer gobs An' I'll tell yer 'boot the worm! ?
 

148 00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,220 
而你身在何处
And where were you?

148
00:09:58,220 --> 00:10:01,900
我们在这里……我们在这里一直到十点一刻和我父亲在码头见面
We were here... We were here until we were to meet my father at the quayside at 10.15...

149
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:08,660
他坚持让我们睡在船里以便捕捉早潮
He insisted we sleep on the boat to catch an early tide.

150
00:10:08,660 --> 00:10:10,820
所以 你昨晚离开旅馆了 什么时候？
So, you left the hotel last night, what time?

151
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:14,380
十点钟 对吗？十点……是
Ten o'clock, yes? Ten...ja.

152
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:17,900
你看见或会见什么人了吗
Did you see or meet anyone?

153
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:20,420
没 没人
No. No-one...

154
00:10:20,420 --> 00:10:23,580
当我父亲半小时后还没出现 我们就回这里了
And when my father doesn't come after half an hour, we come back here.

155
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:25,260
你父亲有个钱包吗
Did your father have a wallet?

156
00:10:25,260 --> 00:10:29,780
是的 在他夹克的内侧口袋里
Yes. The inside pocket of his jacket.

157
00:10:29,780 --> 00:10:31,300
为什么 不见了吗
Why, it is gone?

158
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:33,740
是的 请问
Yes. Could I ask

159
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:36,900
你早前是跟谁在
who were you talking to earlier,

160
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:38,740
打电话？
on the phone?

161
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:40,940
我得通知公司……让他们知情
I had to inform the company... to let them know.

162
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:44,900
我岳父的员工就像一家人
My father-in-law's employees are like his family. Halt du dich da raus.

163
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:49,100
-要给你们护照吧……我这就去拿 -是的
You will be needing our passports... I will go get them for you. Yes.

164
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:53,060
用德语小声交谈
THEY WHISPER IN GERMAN

165
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,380
不好意思
Excuse me,

166
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:58,620
说英语行吗
could you speak in English, please?

167
00:10:58,620 --> 00:11:02,100
抱歉 她英文不太好
Excuse me, her English is not good enough.

168
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:16,700
嗯……我必须……不择手段
Um... I must... By all means.

169
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:26,260
我懂德语 我只是口语不行
I can read German... I just, I can't do the oral.

170
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:31,380
可怜的老艾柯 好了
Poor old Elke. Right.

171
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:35,260
你一旦收集到史迈克的护照就找人追踪查尔纳的下落
Once you've collected the Schmeikels' passports, get someone to track down China...

172
00:11:35,260 --> 00:11:37,900
不管醉醒 我要见他的人 尽快
I want him here drunk or sober, as soon as you can.

173
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:40,140
为什么非得他啊
Why do we need him?

174
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:42,620
只管照做
Just do it, please.

175
00:11:49,860 --> 00:11:52,580
他们在杜伦的大小酒馆找查尔纳了
They're looking in all the pubs in Durham for China.

176
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:55,020
还有病理学家已经开膛破肚了 所以……
And the pathologist's ripping the body open already, so...

177
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:57,420
好了 我们到猪农那里走一趟
Right. Let's visit a pig farmer.

178
00:11:57,420 --> 00:11:59,860
哦 好的
Oh, right.

179
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,380
一分钟
One minute.

180
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:07,140
他们土豪的很 有些猪农
They're pretty well off, some of these pig farmers.

181
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:12,820
这车一百块？ 是
A hundred quid for this car? Yeah.

182
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:18,620
一辆名爵一百磅 性价比高啊！-哦 可不
A hundred pound for an MG is a bargain, man! Oh, yeah,

183
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:21,940
那你为什么贱卖
so why are you selling it so cheap?

184
00:12:21,940 --> 00:12:24,500
你知道的
You know.

185
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:26,820
不宽裕吗 警长
Have you got money problems, Sergeant?

186
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:28,340
没
No.

187
00:12:30,980 --> 00:12:36,380
是 什么？是手头稍紧还是负债累累
Yes. What, are you just feeling the pinch, or are you actually in debt?

188
00:12:38,180 --> 00:12:43,060
-你欠多少 -头儿 这没什么 我应付不了……
How much do you owe? Look, sir, it's nothing I can't manage...

189
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:47,380
-我很快就要参加探长考试了 我会过的…… -嗯 是的我肯定你能行
I'm taking my Inspector's exams soon...which I'll pass... Well, yes, I'm sure you'll pass.

190
00:12:47,380 --> 00:12:50,780
但最近又没职位空缺
But I can't see a vacancy for an Inspector coming up in the near future.

191
00:12:50,780 --> 00:12:54,060
呃 等有了我就会调到另一个部门去了
Well, then I'll transfer to another force where they've got more room.

192
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:57,420
更大的地方 那得多久
Somewhere bigger. And how long's that going to take?

193
00:12:57,420 --> 00:12:59,660
看吧 头儿 一切尽在掌握
Look, Sir, it's all in hand.

194
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:04,460
是 不错……因为对负债的警察而言 遍地是诱惑
Yeah, good...because a copper in debt is open to temptation.

195
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:08,500
实际上 我反感那么做 什么？你觉得不会发生在你身上？
I resent that, actually. What? You think it can't happen to you?

196
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:13,460
屡见不鲜 多少锦绣前程就此断送
I've seen it a dozen times. A dozen promising careers ruined.

197
00:13:13,460 --> 00:13:16,220
友情建议 仅此而已
Just trying to offer some friendly advice.

198
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:18,740
是 头儿 收到 “切勿负债”
Yes, sir, I heard your advice. "Don't get into debt".

199
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:21,500
谢您的小贴士 我都在卖车了 不是？
Thanks for the tip. I'm selling me car, aren't I?

200
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:24,060
抱歉抱歉
Sorry. Sorry.

201
00:13:25,500 --> 00:13:29,260
老实讲 船到桥头自然直
Honestly, it'll all get straightened out.

202
00:13:37,260 --> 00:13:41,380
我觉得史迈克夫人欲言又止
I reckon Mrs Schmeikel knows more than she's allowed to say.

203
00:13:51,220 --> 00:13:53,020
哦 什么味道
Oh, what's that smell?!

204
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:59,260
鞋子……
Shoes...

205
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:04,460
你们谁啊 想干啥 警探巴克斯
Who are yous, like, and what d'yer want? Detective Sergeant Bacchus...

206
00:14:04,460 --> 00:14:08,980
怎么了 爹？那个屁精是谁？公子哥似的
How, Da! Who's that flash bugger? Looks like a toff.

207
00:14:08,980 --> 00:14:11,180
下午
Afternoon.

208
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:16,860
我是詹特利总督察 这是巴克斯警探
I'm Detective Chief Inspector Gently. This is Detective Sergeant Bacchus.

209
00:14:16,860 --> 00:14:18,500
我们想问你一些问题 麻烦了
We'd like to ask you a few questions, please.

210
00:14:18,500 --> 00:14:21,420
一个伦敦佬！还是大人物
A bloody Londoner! And a big-wig an' all.

211
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:25,580
不能更糟了！欢迎来到南北分界 先生
Gets worse and worse! Welcome to the North/South divide, sir.

212
00:14:25,580 --> 00:14:29,820
好吧 我正要去用餐……所以不想在那干等的话就进来
Well, I'm just about to have me dinner...so either wait there, or away in.

213
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:40,500
我震惊了……
I'm shocked...shocked,

214
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:42,740
我很震惊
I am, I'm shocked.

215
00:14:42,740 --> 00:14:48,220
是的 我们昨晚和他一起
I am. We were with him last night!

216
00:14:48,220 --> 00:14:49,900
谁会干掉冈特？！
Who'd wanna do Gunter?!

217
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:53,580
没人……为什么他们要这样？！
Naybody...why would they?!

218
00:14:53,580 --> 00:14:57,180
我们开走的时候跟他招手了
I gave him a wave as we drove off!

219
00:14:57,180 --> 00:14:58,700
我吃不下去了
I can barely eat!

220
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:04,340
我能问你昨晚的事吗
Can I ask you about last night?

221
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:07,700
嗯 随便你问
Aye, ask what yer like, aye!

222
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:09,740
你去了船员休息室
You went to the Mariners.

223
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:14,380
是 怎么了
Aye! And what happened?

224
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:17,380
因为自从冈特被编宿以来我就没见过他了
Cos I haven't seen Gunter since he was billeted here...

225
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:21,420
但只要他一回来 就会到他的小阁楼里 仍然像个战犯
But as soon as he's back, he's back in his loft where he was as a PoW...

226
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:26,380
他在那儿睡了两晚 猪场里的各种事情他也帮忙
Two nights he slept there. He helps out with the pigs an' everything...

227
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:29,220
现在他是个截然不同的农民了
Him an altogether different type of farmer now...

228
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:36,620
一名制药商 是啊 一名制药商 对
A pharmaceutical man. Aye, a pharmaceutical man, that's right, aye.

229
00:15:36,620 --> 00:15:39,540
但他做事就像二十年前那样 你知道 他乐在其中
But he mucks in like it's 20 years ago, you know, and he loves it.

230
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:44,460
我们带他去哈德良城墙……因为我教他怎么成为鸟人
We took him to Hadrian's Wall...cos I taught him to be a bird man,

231
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:49,140
很少有鸟飞来 你知道 有很多事要干
and there's rare ones flying in, you know, quite a to-do about it,

232
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:53,500
你们知道这是他的最后一晚 我们都在馆子里
and 'fore yer know it's his last night and we're all in the pub.

233
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:55,100
所有酒水都是他请
He's buying drinks for everybody.

234
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:00,700
不 真的 你已经请得够多了
No, really, already you have given enough!

235
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:04,420
那我明天走的时候
Then, when I'm gone, tomorrow,

236
00:16:04,420 --> 00:16:08,660
全场还是算我的！一杯淡黑 先生 谢谢！
the drinks are still on me! One Black and Tan, sir. Thank you!

237
00:16:08,660 --> 00:16:10,260
不用找了
Keep it, please.

238
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:11,860
唱虫歌！
Singing the Worm song!

239
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:14,460
是 是
Aye. Aye...

240
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:16,260
他现在要告诉你们虫的一切
He'll tell yer all about the worm now.

241
00:16:16,260 --> 00:16:23,100
别出声 伙计们 为了请你们喝酒的男人保持呼吸 冈特・史迈克！
Whisht lads and hold yer gobs for the man who's buyin' drinks, Gunter Schmeikel!

242
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:25,580
必胜……必胜！
Sieg heil... Sieg heil!

243
00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:27,660
哦诶！不要记恨 你们！
Oy! Forgive and forget, you lot!

244
00:16:27,660 --> 00:16:30,260
否则我扇你巴掌！
Or I'll slap yer chops for yer!

245
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:32,060
麦布斯
Mabs...

246
00:16:32,060 --> 00:16:33,260
麦布斯 这全是开玩笑的！
Mabs, it's all in jest!

247
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:40,700
他钓到一条鱼 他觉得很稀奇
?He catched a fish upon his heuk He thought leukt varry queer

248
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:46,620
是哪一种鱼儿 年轻的兰普顿不知道
?But what'n a kind of fish it was Young Lambton couldn't tell

249
00:16:46,620 --> 00:16:52,340
他不急着带它回家 就把它放在井下
?He wasn't fash to carry it home So he hoyed it doon a well

250
00:16:52,340 --> 00:16:58,420
别出声 伙计们 吸口气 让我告诉你一件可怕的事
?Whisht lads, hold yer gobs I'll tell yer all an awful story

251
00:16:58,420 --> 00:17:04,660

别出声 伙计们 吸口气 让我告诉你踢走虫子的事
?Whisht lads, hold yer gobs, I'll tell yer boot the worm! ?
 253 00:17:05,820 --> 00:17:09,460 Fancy a drop of home brew, Chief Inspector?!

252
00:17:09,460 --> 00:17:11,580
是 非常好 谢谢
Yeah, be very nice. Thank you.

253
00:17:11,580 --> 00:17:15,380
他就像冈特的家人 是吧
He's like Gunter's family, isn't he?

254
00:17:15,380 --> 00:17:19,300
什么 他说你是冈特一伙的
What was that? He says you're a lot like Gunter.

255
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:23,340
不是轰炸机飞行员了吧你？哦 不 不是轰炸机飞行员了 不
Weren't a bomber pilot, though, were yer? Oh, no. Not a bomber pilot, no.

256
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:25,940
不 你要像个轰炸机飞行员样 上点档次！
No, you gotta be posh to be a bomber pilot!

257
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:29,660
不是那套保守党派的上档次……
Not yer Alec Douglas-Home posh...

258
00:17:29,660 --> 00:17:32,140
但是比你强
But posher than you.

259
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:34,020
是啊 他会喜欢你的
Aye, he'd have liked you.

260
00:17:34,020 --> 00:17:37,580
你也会喜欢他 好吧 人人都爱老冈特
You'd have liked him, well, everybody liked Gunter.

261
00:17:37,580 --> 00:17:39,900
晚上结束的时候发生什么了？- 他要回德国
End of the evening, what happened? Well, he's back to Deutschland

262
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:43,420
早潮的时候 所以我们从馆子出来 拥抱他
first tide, so we come out the pub and give him a hug.

263
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:46,060
那是几点？
What time was that?

264
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:49,860
十点整……我们起得早 你知道的
Ten o'clock sharp... We're up early in the morning, you know.

265
00:17:49,860 --> 00:17:51,740
从哪条路回家的
Which way did you go home?

266
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:55,380
-沿着码头返回山上的 -看见其他人了吗
Along the quayside and back up the hill. See anybody else?

267
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:58,060
我想没有 不对 有 我们看到了！
Don't think so, no. Yeah, we did!

268
00:17:58,060 --> 00:18:01,580
他的儿子 在旅馆附近
That son of his, near his hotel.

269
00:18:01,580 --> 00:18:04,300
因为我说了句“你跟他走岔了”
Cos I said, "Oh, you've missed him!"

270
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:06,620
我很抱歉 但他不待见咱们
I'm sorry, but he didn't like us.

271
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:08,420
啊 你也不喜欢他……我们注意到了！
Ah, you didn't like him... We noticed!

272
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:11,660
谁会喜欢那个自大狂？
Well, what's to like about that arrogant shite?

273
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:16,780
所以你看见他和妻子沿着码头走
So you saw him and his wife walking towards the quayside.

274
00:18:16,780 --> 00:18:19,500
不不 她不在 就他一个人
No, no, she wasn't with him. He was on his own...

275
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:22,540
难道她不会…… 她胆小
Wouldn't have her down...she's just a mouse.

276
00:18:27,380 --> 00:18:29,820
有什么需要的 尽管叫我
Anything I can do, just give us a shout!

277
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:31,340
谢谢
Thank you.

278
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:37,940
-你看到那个在周围晃悠的年轻小伙子了吗 左边那个 -看到了
Did you see the young lad skulking around? The one that left. I did...

279
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:40,780
说曹操曹操到
Speak of the devil.

280
00:18:40,780 --> 00:18:42,740
昨晚在酒馆
In the pub last night.

281
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:49,260
酒吧后面有个新来的小伙子叫夏弗斯
There was this new bloke behind the bar called Shavers...

282
00:18:49,260 --> 00:18:51,900
一个大混蛋 你不会去招惹他的
A big bastard, like, yer wouldn't cross him.

283
00:18:53,740 --> 00:18:56,100
不管怎样 我们和冈特在一起
Anyway, we're with Gunter.

284
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:59,900
在酒吧的我一哥们说夏弗斯语不惊人死不休纳粹那些事
A mate of mine at the bar says Shavers has been mouthing off

285
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:04,340
在冈特的啤酒里小便 还放言道要做得更甚 知道吗
about the Nazis an' that, an' how he pissed in Gunter's beer and said he had a mind to do more, you know?

286
00:19:08,300 --> 00:19:12,540
当一些人走出来抗议 他的走狗就跟着他
And when a few others walked out in protest, he gans with 'em.

287
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:16,980
-别出声 伙计们 吸口气 让我告诉你一件可怕的事 -这是几点的事
?Whisht lads, hold yer gobs I'll tell yer all an awful story... ?
What time was this?

288
00:19:16,980 --> 00:19:18,700
刚过九点？
Just after nine?

289
00:19:20,260 --> 00:19:23,180
好吧 谢了…… 保持联系
Right, thanks... We'll be in touch.

290
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:25,460
在我们要走的时候我又看见他了
I saw him again that night when we were leaving.

291
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:29,500
在停车场
In the car park,

292
00:19:29,500 --> 00:19:33,820
背阴的地方 观察咱们……我感觉不妙 就像 但……
in the shadows, watching us... I didn't have a good feeling, like, but...

293
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:37,860
和冈特道别后再回头看 他就不见了
say goodbye to Gunter and look back, and he'd gone.

294
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:39,580
是夏弗斯？
This is Shavers?

295
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:42,140
是啊
Aye.

296
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:45,020
奇克・夏弗斯 你看见他往哪走了吗
Chick Shavers. Did you see where he went?

297
00:19:46,540 --> 00:19:48,300
没 我们只是开走了
Nah, we just drove off.

298
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:50,300
之后看见什么人没？
And did you see anyone after that?

299
00:19:50,300 --> 00:19:52,580
只有鞋子上的狗屎
Only Dog Shite On Yer Shoe.

300
00:19:54,180 --> 00:19:57,260
你知道 冈特的儿子 从山上下来
Y'know, Gunter's son. Coming down the hill.

301
00:19:57,260 --> 00:19:58,900
谢谢
Thank you.

302
00:19:58,900 --> 00:20:01,380
谢了
Thanks.

303
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:02,820
嘿！
Hoy!

304
00:20:02,820 --> 00:20:05,420
你知道开车的小诀窍吗
Y'know that owld knack ya drivin'?

305
00:20:05,420 --> 00:20:07,980
25镑买废品？
Will you take 25 pound for scrap?

306
00:20:07,980 --> 00:20:09,220
不 我不愿意
No. I won't.

307
00:20:12,380 --> 00:20:16,060
你再碰我试试！进来
Touch me one more time! Get in.

308
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:18,740
夏弗斯先生 感谢您前来 请坐
Mr Shavers, thanks for coming in. Please sit down.

309
00:20:18,740 --> 00:20:21,340
不 谢了 我不会停下来的
No, ta, I won't be stopping.

310
00:20:23,820 --> 00:20:30,340
有人举报声称你曾在一位特别顾客的啤酒里排便
e've had reports that you claimed to have urinated in the beer of a particular customer last night...

311
00:20:30,340 --> 00:20:36,300
在克劳特 是啊 我干了三次呢 一个帝国一次！
In the Kraut's, aye. I did it three times, one for each Reich!

312
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:38,340
你清楚史迈克先生今早被发现死亡了吧
You're aware Mr Schmeikel was found dead this morning.

313
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:41,420
呃 如果死因是尿液中毒 你们抓到人了
Well, if it's from urine poisoning, I'm yer man.

314
00:20:41,420 --> 00:20:44,620
他死没死你毫不关心？看
You don't mind that he's dead? Look.

315
00:20:44,620 --> 00:20:48,500
我不知道战争期间你做了什么 坐下 向民众大放厥词 释放隔阂的烟幕……
I don't know what you were doing in the war. Sit down. Yelling at folk to put up black-out curtains...

316
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:54,620
我是把那些渣滓从哪来的踢回哪去 还有我亲眼所见 有事长埋于此 于此！
I was kicking that scum back where they came from, and I saw things that are buried into here! Here!

317
00:20:54,620 --> 00:20:57,660
你和你们世界的其他人可以原谅忘记 但不包括我
You and the rest of the world can forgive and forget... But not me.

