I'll put piss in their beer, and folk'll pat us on the back for doing it!

345
00:22:31,540 --> 00:22:34,540
-你还干了什么了？ -你什么意思，还？
-What else did you do? -What d'you mean, what else?

346
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:38,180
我们有目击证人说在冈特・施麦克离开酒馆时你在停车场
We have a witness that places you in the car park when Gunter Schmeikel left the pub.

347
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:41,740
证人？你不是说那个弱智吧？
Witness. Don't yer mean half-wit?

