01:20:55,420 --> 01:20:57,780
But that still left us with the same problem.

1186
01:20:57,780 --> 01:20:59,900
Me wife and Alice, cos with me in prison,

1187
01:20:59,900 --> 01:21:03,020
them two's put away in mental homes and...

