1210
01:22:29,980 --> 01:22:32,420
Well, like everything in life, you need the luck.

1211
01:22:32,420 --> 01:22:34,940
I figured rich folk like that would be staying at the hotel

1212
01:22:34,940 --> 01:22:35,980
